              "port": "{{reverb_port}}",
              "path": ["app", "{{reverb_app_key}}"]
            },
            "description": "## Send this in User B's WebSocket tab to unsubscribe:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"event\": \"pusher:unsubscribe\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"channel\": \"presence-conversation.1\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## User A's tab should receive:\n```json\n{\n  \"event\": \"pusher_internal:member_removed\",\n  \"channel\": \"presence-conversation.1\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"user_id\": 2\n  }\n}\n```\n\nAlternatively, just close the User B WebSocket tab — same member_removed event fires."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "INSTRUCTION: Reconnect User B — observe member_added",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"event\": \"pusher:subscribe\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"channel\": \"presence-conversation.{{conversation_id}}\",\n    \"auth\": \"{{channel_auth_b}}\",\n    \"channel_data\": \"{{channel_data_b}}\"\n  }\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "ws://{{reverb_host}}:{{reverb_port}}/app/{{reverb_app_key}}",
              "protocol": "ws",
              "host": ["{{reverb_host}}"],
              "port": "{{reverb_port}}",
              "path": ["app", "{{reverb_app_key}}"]
            },
            "description": "Re-subscribe User B. User A's tab should receive:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"event\": \"pusher_internal:member_added\",\n  \"channel\": \"presence-conversation.1\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"user_id\": 2,\n    \"user_info\": { \"id\": 2, \"name\": \"User B\", \"image\": \"...\" }\n  }\n}\n```\n\nThis is used by clients to show online/active status for conversation participants.\n\n**Note:** Re-subscribing requires a fresh channel auth if the old one has expired (they expire with the socket connection)."
          }
        }
